{"tid":441147,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【原創音樂台】這輩子，我只想跟妳在一起《只有妳一個》MV","createTime":"2017-10-19T11:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T17:15:17.000Z","uid":50360,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b1630f02093040d44b6c4a32e6b6325e31689d6a","tid":441147,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:37:55.000Z","msg":"嗯...依首原創歌曲，係十年前已經寫好，係一首小說主題曲。十年後，我重新修訂自己寫嘅小說做《南區之戀Remake》，依首歌亦由十年前嘅封印解除。<br />\n<br />\n有幾多曾經視另一半為只有妳一個，到依家依個人仍然係身邊陪住你？<br />\n<br />\n《只有妳一個》MV：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cDaaBE1iXdQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcDaaBE1iXdQ&d=SFdoF744aWed7kNU3WVg7v6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=7a6ec041\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cDaaBE1iXdQ</a>"},{"pid":"4029fe32cac22e21afa4d6d019ed644d4bdfdaf5","tid":441147,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:38:28.000Z","msg":"《只有妳一個》〈《南區之戀．下半部Remake大結局主題曲》〉<br />\n<br />\n作曲：劉啟俊<br />\n填詞：陳炳洋<br />\n編曲：劉啟俊<br />\n主唱：挽歌之聲<br />\n<br />\n每次碰上痛苦亦有妳伴我<br />\n遇寂寞便獨坐沙灘觀晚浪  唯獨妳肯一起跟我坐<br />\n放棄妳照顧她是我太笨  令妳慟哭過<br />\n拭淚後仍入微待我即使惹禍 <br />\n承受太多  令我更憎我<br />\n<br />\n原來只得妳這一個  無條件偏愛珍惜我<br />\n即使多辛苦  總有著妳愛我  甚至肯原諒我的錯 <br />\n情人只得妳這一個  旁人即使話我很傻 <br />\n不管多少劫禍降  仍然陪伴同坐<br />\n<br />\n對愛欠缺信心自信變自我<br />\n為避熱烈待我築起的冷漠  唯獨妳不擔心遭冷落<br />\n告訴我愛妳總是太怯懦  像勇氣乾涸<br />\n棄用動人話詞換上心聲配樂<br />\n憑住這歌  示意愛一個<br />\n<br />\n原來只得妳這一個  無條件偏愛珍惜我<br />\n即使多辛苦  總有著妳愛我  甚至肯原諒我的錯 <br />\n情人只得妳這一個  旁人即使話我很傻 <br />\n不管多少劫禍降  仍然陪伴同坐<br />\n<br />\n過去我背負太多  然而由今天竟失去更多<br />\n我也太蠢竟守信往日承諾  從前令妳我錯失過<br />\n<br />\n原來只得妳這一個  無條件偏愛珍惜我<br />\n多少的苦果  不會讓我察覺  沉默地嚐盡每一個<br />\n情人只得妳這一個  無人犧牲像妳般傻<br />\n只懂擔心顧慮我  隨時隨地陪我<br />\n<br />\n從來只得妳這心愛  無人可取締的一個<br />\n當非走不可  失去令我發覺  害怕跟離別上一課 <br />\n明明不捨去拋低我  然而傷心無法消亡<br />\n心知即將告別我  如何承受難過<br />\n<br />\n沿途緊握對方不放  才能牽手渡過將來<br />\n即使擔驚畏懼過  仍然陪伴行過"},{"pid":"624166ad20664a0d69963510ef0cda92b8fc6df4","tid":441147,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T12:16:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3bac57d944fce4449578931dcd00f0337a6d16","tid":441147,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T13:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b70374989b6f885d8f9d447afdfd2de44e7502","tid":441147,"uid":136023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa822c727e230bda4bca58bf80cef2c0f16a5c6","tid":441147,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:06:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f9d08f2a5a314e62cabe8a057ebddd5db006152","tid":441147,"uid":154456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:07:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb61dfdc73272520b0dd49ea1a2171b43a8fc35d","tid":441147,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:13:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>躝返紅登啦垃圾<br />\n想食兩家茶禮你當人傻?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d6a782d2218d01ab84424b8df41665078e7a95a","tid":441147,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB